text: Patrice Gélard (3 August 1938 – 25 June 2020) was a French politician. He was a member of the Senate of France. He represented the Seine-Maritime. He was a member of the Union for a Popular Movement (UMP) Party. Gélard died on 25 June 2020 at the age of 81. ==References== ==Other websites== *Page on the Senate website Category:1938 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Politicians from Normandy Category:People from Seine-Maritime
